{
  "nodes": [
    {
      "id": "file:Engine/src/Himii/Events/Event.h",
      "type": "file",
      "name": "Event.h",
      "filePath": "Engine/src/Himii/Events/Event.h",
      "summary": "引擎事件系统的核心头文件，定义事件基类 Event 和事件分发器 EventDispatcher，以及 EventType/EventCategory 枚举和 EVENT_CLASS_TYPE/EVENT_CLASS_CATEGORY 宏，为所有具体事件类型提供统一的抽象接口和类型安全分发机制。",
      "tags": ["event-system", "base-class", "core", "macro-based", "event-dispatcher"],
      "complexity": "moderate",
      "languageNotes": "使用 EVENT_CLASS_TYPE 和 EVENT_CLASS_CATEGORY 宏实现类 CRTP 模式，在子类中自动生成 GetStaticType/GetEventType/GetName/GetCategoryFlags 方法，避免样板代码重复。"
    },
    {
      "id": "file:Engine/src/Himii/Events/ApplicationEvent.h",
      "type": "file",
      "name": "ApplicationEvent.h",
      "filePath": "Engine/src/Himii/Events/ApplicationEvent.h",
      "summary": "定义应用程序生命周期相关的事件类，包括窗口关闭事件 WindowCloseEvent 和窗口大小调整事件 WindowResizeEvent，均继承自 Event 基类并通过宏声明事件类型和分类。",
      "tags": ["event-system", "window-event", "application-lifecycle"],
      "complexity": "simple"
    },
    {
      "id": "file:Engine/src/Himii/Events/KeyEvent.h",
      "type": "file",
      "name": "KeyEvent.h",
      "filePath": "Engine/src/Himii/Events/KeyEvent.h",
      "summary": "定义键盘输入事件的四层继承层次：键盘事件基类 KeyEvent（存储按键码）及其三个子类——按键按下 KeyPressedEvent（支持重复标志）、按键释放 KeyReleasedEvent 和字符输入 KeyTypedEvent。",
      "tags": ["event-system", "keyboard-input", "inheritance-hierarchy", "input-handling"],
      "complexity": "moderate"
    },
    {
      "id": "file:Engine/src/Himii/Events/MouseEvent.h",
      "type": "file",
      "name": "MouseEvent.h",
      "filePath": "Engine/src/Himii/Events/MouseEvent.h",
      "summary": "定义鼠标输入事件的五类继承层次：鼠标移动 MouseMovedEvent（携带坐标）、鼠标滚轮 MouseScrolledEvent（携带偏移量），以及三个鼠标按键相关事件（抽象基类 MouseButtonEvent 及其按下/释放子类）。",
      "tags": ["event-system", "mouse-input", "inheritance-hierarchy", "input-handling"],
      "complexity": "moderate"
    },
    {
      "id": "class:Engine/src/Himii/Events/Event.h:Event",
      "type": "class",
      "name": "Event",
      "filePath": "Engine/src/Himii/Events/Event.h",
      "lineRange": [39, 58],
      "summary": "所有事件的抽象基类，定义纯虚接口 GetEventType()、GetName()、GetCategoryFlags()，以及虚方法 ToString() 和内联方法 IsInCategroy()，并包含公共字段 Handled 用于标记事件是否已被处理。",
      "tags": ["base-class", "abstract-class", "virtual-interface", "event-system"],
      "complexity": "moderate"
    },
    {
      "id": "class:Engine/src/Himii/Events/Event.h:EventDispatcher",
      "type": "class",
      "name": "EventDispatcher",
      "filePath": "Engine/src/Himii/Events/Event.h",
      "lineRange": [60, 79],
      "summary": "事件分发模板类，通过模板方法 Dispatch 实现类型安全的事件分发：利用静态多态（T::GetStaticType()）匹配事件具体类型后，将基类引用 static_cast 为具体类型并调用处理函数。",
      "tags": ["event-dispatcher", "template-class", "type-dispatch", "crtp-pattern"],
      "complexity": "simple"
    },
    {
      "id": "class:Engine/src/Himii/Events/ApplicationEvent.h:WindowCloseEvent",
      "type": "class",
      "name": "WindowCloseEvent",
      "filePath": "Engine/src/Himii/Events/ApplicationEvent.h",
      "lineRange": [7, 11],
      "summary": "窗口关闭事件，继承自 Event 基类，无额外数据负载，仅通过宏携带 WindowClose 事件类型和 Application 事件分类标志位。",
      "tags": ["window-event", "event-system", "application-lifecycle"],
      "complexity": "simple"
    },
    {
      "id": "class:Engine/src/Himii/Events/ApplicationEvent.h:WindowResizeEvent",
      "type": "class",
      "name": "WindowResizeEvent",
      "filePath": "Engine/src/Himii/Events/ApplicationEvent.h",
      "lineRange": [13, 33],
      "summary": "窗口大小调整事件，继承自 Event 基类，携带新的宽度和高度信息，提供 GetWidth() 和 GetHeight() 访问器获取调整后的窗口尺寸。",
      "tags": ["window-event", "event-system", "application-lifecycle", "data-payload"],
      "complexity": "simple"
    },
    {
      "id": "class:Engine/src/Himii/Events/KeyEvent.h:KeyEvent",
      "type": "class",
      "name": "KeyEvent",
