      "lineRange": [7, 21],
      "summary": "键盘事件抽象基类，继承自 Event，存储按键码 m_KeyCode 并提供 GetKeyCode() 访问器，分类为 Input 和 Keyboard 事件。构造函数声明为 protected，仅允许子类实例化。",
      "tags": ["base-class", "keyboard-input", "event-system", "protected-constructor"],
      "complexity": "simple"
    },
