      "lineRange": [23, 42],
      "summary": "按键按下事件，继承自 KeyEvent，新增重复按键标志位 m_IsRepeat 和 IsRepeat() 访问器，重写 ToString() 输出按键码和重复状态信息。",
      "tags": ["keyboard-input", "event-system", "event-data", "inheritance"],
      "complexity": "simple"
    },
